content.html: I used to work at a jewellers. A man came in and said, "Have you got a potato clock?". I said, "Never heard of it, but we have carriage clocks and cuckoo clocks". He said, "That's no good, you see I have a new job that starts at 9, and my wife said I need to get a potato clock".
